quests.desc: Welcome to TextWorld! Here is your task for today. First thing I need you to do is to head south. With that done, head west. That done, attempt to venture west. And then, travel west. If you can do that, attempt to go west. And then, make an attempt to head south. After that, make an effort to take a trip east. Once you manage that, make an effort to head east. And then, venture east. With that over with, recover the keycard from the rack within the cookhouse. Alright, thanks!
